If You Are Looking For A Home With The Master On The Main Or If You Want a Home that is Comfortable to Host Gatherings, This Home Is It. This Open Floor Concept Features 4 Beds 2.5 Baths With The Master on the Main. Over 50k of Upgrades. Stainless Steel Appliances & High Quality Finishes. Oversized Garage Could Be Used For Camper/Boat Storage. Tankless Water Heater & Water Softener System. Tucked Back In A Cul De Sac, This Smaller Neighborhood Backs To A Nature Reserve with Walking Trails And Is Close To Amenities. Request An Amenities List for Upgrades.
